## Phase 5 — MCP Server

Replace AI-instruction-based memory writes with a typed MCP server. The skill/README install method remains the primary bootstrap; MCP becomes the runtime layer once installed.

### 5.1 Core lib layer
- [x] `mcp/src/lib/note.ts` — Note type + parse/serialize (rating, created, last_used, concepts, sources, body)
- [x] `mcp/src/lib/storage.ts` — Read/write thoughts.md, tree.md, changes.md, @plan (atomic file writes)
- [x] `mcp/src/lib/git.ts` — pull --rebase, add -A, commit, push via simple-git
- [x] `mcp/src/config.ts` — Parse @brain YAML config, resolve BRAIN_ROOT from @pinky line 1

